<HEADLINE> Zimbabwe to Keep Reforming Civil Service  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Moyo told provincial heads, captains of industry and commerce
in Bulawayo that "we cannot run this economy when the civil
service becomes inefficient and does not perform accordingly," he
said.
