Rusdihardjo of his post as National Police (POLRI) chief and
appointed Let. Gen. Bimantoro as care taker of the post.
</P>
<P>
"I have told Vice President Megawati Soekarnoputri and
Commander of the Indonesian Defense Forces (TNI) Admiral Widodo AS
about this matter," the President told the press at the Merdeka
