recently that replacement of the national police chief should be
agreed upon by the House of Representatives (DPR). But the law on
the implementation of the decree has not yet been made and that
the deputy chief of POLRI should take care of the job.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile, Wahid denied the rumors that he will replace TNI
chief Widodo in connection with the bomb blast occurred at the
Jakarta Stock Exchange last Wednesday in which 15 people were
killed.
</P>
<P>
"There is no plan for that," he said. 
