winning way, upsetting the more fancied team from China in four
sets 25-23, 26-28, 25-20 and 25-15 in the women's volleyball
preliminaries of the Olympic Games on Monday.
</P>
<P>
The youthful Croatians had their opposition's measure and
continued to grow in confidence as the match progressed.
</P>
