kills and Elana Cebukina's blocking. Another highlight was the
emergence of 17-year-old Biljana Gligorovic, showing maturity
beyond her years as she controlled the Croatian attack.
</P>
<P>
China continued to disappoint as the Olympic silver medallists
battled to overcome their inconsistencies. Captain Sun Yue and Wu
Yongmei lifted China to take the second, but this was small
consolation as the side withered under the pressure of the
Croatian game.
</P>
<P>
China will need to regroup quickly before their next match
against Brazil as another loss would be devastating to its
confidence. Croatia will play the United States in an eagerly
anticipated match. 
